{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"6174","heading":"Future-years defense environmental cleanup plan","label":"6174 Future-years defense environmental cleanup plan","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/stA/ptVI/sptB/ch604/schI","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","Prior ProvisionsProvisions similar to those in this section were contained in , War and National Defense, prior to repeal by .section 2582a of Title 50Pub. L. 119–60, § 3111(b)(1)"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—In General","label":"a .—In General","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/a/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fa%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"reflects the estimated expenditures and proposed appropriations included in that budget for the Department of Energy for defense environmental cleanup; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/a/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fa%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"covers a period that includes the fiscal year for which that budget is submitted and not less than the four succeeding fiscal years.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Elements","label":"b .—Elements","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A detailed description of the projects and activities relating to defense environmental cleanup to be carried out during the period covered by the plan at the sites specified in subsection (c) and with respect to the activities specified in subsection (d).","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A statement of proposed budget authority, estimated expenditures, and proposed appropriations necessary to support such projects and activities.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/3/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fb%2F3%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"A statement of each milestone included in an enforceable agreement governing cleanup and waste remediation for that site for each fiscal year covered by the plan.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fb%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For each such milestone, a statement with respect to whether each such milestone will be met in each such fiscal year.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"C","heading":null,"label":"C","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/3/C","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fb%2F3%2FC","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For any milestone that will not be met, an explanation of why the milestone will not be met and the date by which the milestone is expected to be met.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"D","heading":null,"label":"D","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/3/D","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/b/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fb%2F3%2FD","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"For any milestone that has been missed, renegotiated, or postponed, a statement of the current milestone, the original milestone, and any interim milestones.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"c","heading":".—Sites Specified","label":"c .—Sites Specified","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fc","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fc%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Idaho National Laboratory, Idaho.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fc%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Waste Isolation Pilot Plant, Carlsbad, New Mexico.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fc%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Savannah River Site, Aiken, South Carolina.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft10%2Fs6174%2Fc%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"The Oak Ridge National Laboratory, Oak Ridge, Tennessee.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t10/s6174/c","sourc